{
  "stem": "17426.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 58.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the sound came closer and closer and closer to us until it finally stopped.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were singing a very well-known school song that almost everyone who went in Poland to school knew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was something like, 'Today we are together, tomorrow we will be separated, and each one will go his own way,' and something, you know, along this line of what graduation of school has-- a graduation song, really.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I sat, and I kept my eyes closed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just was hoping that it wasn't a dream, that this was real, that it will repeat itself, that I hear the song again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when I opened my eyes, there were five young ladies, young girls, looking at us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And inquisitively, they came over to us and asked who we were, what we doing here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was the first labor camp in the region of Poznan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was one camp that was established shortly before us, about a month before us, in Poznan itself, at the stadium.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this was outside Poznan, something like 20 kilometers outside Poznan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were not-- they have never seen-- Poznan wasn't very Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, these girls, except for one, didn't even know what a Jew was or have seen a Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were small-town girls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they worked in a-- in a nursery, in a garden nursery there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they left with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] that they had when they heard what we have gone through the last two days when we ordered inducted in this camp, and how we were treated, how badly, you know, what they are doing with us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took such pity on us that they brought us food every day, and we carried it back to the Baustelle, to the work place.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
